Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title}Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I call you the Old Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom is {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scythe dude calls me Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, Zwei, Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need an explanation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nice to meet you"? I see the title of Phantom has degraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I could kill you whenever I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wouldn't be fun, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding you two. Driving you into a corner. Killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the only things that have kept me alive for the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being kept by that fucking Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please let me enjoy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you two being afraid and running for your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And will that make you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've seen Reiji's face when he saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like he saw a ghost or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I kill you in front of Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of face do you think he'll make?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll kill you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're well prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing yourself to protect Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so damn lovable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that's lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't forget the fact that Reiji abandoned you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make him regret more. You want to bury him in sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not the Reiji you knew back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He threw away his past and lives for the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a ghost of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand in his way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk as if you know him pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand how strong-willed he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the main character enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen, Cal, you have no reason to fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, it seems like you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire cast hasn't gathered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you already abandon me once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time won't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'll take this woman with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take her with me to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ, I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Japan, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can just get away after shooting in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shoot, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do that, I'll kill everyone in here including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're first, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your gun and get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a boring ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your successor, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm her support.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her, I don't feel alive every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the game of school is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization discovered your whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry, but I don't have the confidence to stop that crazy bitch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live in the present, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Clau's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl and me... if you had to pick one of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll secure the escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During this period, we'll let Inferno handle Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time to shuffle the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you've got a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he calls himself Claudia's confidant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years, Shiga Toru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia McCunnen's confidant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Asian brat that was always by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, it's the assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're being hunted down by the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Shinokura High School ring any bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinokura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school that the daughter of Godoh Kaiten goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know what the fuck you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're touching something that you're not supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as nothing happens to us, we won't lay a hand on Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as nothing happens to us that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno's assassin is after me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want you to stop her, Shiga Toru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put pressure on the Inferno presence in Japan with your authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you whether you do it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you became an actor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing compared to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this works out, we can gain enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga's a sharp guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely do as we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this doesn't work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll think of other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to endanger Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy that Drei is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she died on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:11:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I killed her by getting her involved with what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'm going north at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a smuggling freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go and negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay with Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner as soon as we get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received orders from the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems like you've heard about it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godoh Group's godfather - Godoh Kaiten's secret child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like those two didn't become students because they felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a fuck about Japan's yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godoh Group is also an official part of Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Godoh princess can't be safely secured,\Nthere's no way to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were deceived by Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for the next chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bodyguard for a high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me and to the Group,\N she's an extremely important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a need to deploy us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your lives to protect her! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate him that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the fuck do you think I've been listening to the orders of this shitty organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I want find and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can bear to watch you and Zwei fight, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're underestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he lied to a lot of people two years ago and messed around with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he's a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were the exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been lying to me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never told me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He covered up his lies with more lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just scared of the moment when he wouldn't be able to keep me in the dark anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lied in order to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one he ever wanted to protect was himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he abandoned me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And ran away with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that can't be your reason to be an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being one because you want to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm the great Phantom who can even make a crying brat shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gangs who own the streets will shiver when they hear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicking those bastards around, tormenting them, killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have a better life than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He realized that I would become too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely pay him back for lying to me and using me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, you're just like burnt-out fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen's absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's had a fever since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might just be a cold though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've gone to your house and taken that cold away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're talking about boring stuff as usual, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we're going to a movie today and I'm allowing you guys to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you invite someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they ditched us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Sanae say everyone's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a way to beat around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Elen gets better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just be a bother to Elen if I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I move around with Fujieda Mio,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga will be pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fooling around like a kid. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That movie was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should thank Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your views are different from those of normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's ordinary and normal to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something that you treasure dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when I look at you, I fall in love with the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's something boring, it has its own significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that everyone has forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I intruding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's Fujieda Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, me, and the princess of the Godoh Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use each and every woman that gets close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have any intentions of harming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's continue our match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can be only one true Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Phantom, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm just a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that type of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want my life, then I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you escaping up until today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't want to die. You just wanted to keep living. Wasn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill me, I'll gladly accept that as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something that merits you killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking my life, I want you stop hunting Elen-... Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be her scapegoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be a threat to Scythe or Inferno anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to protect her even if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After abandoning me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you have someone else that's so important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'll continue to torture you and make you feel pain before I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ghosts that cannot exist anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are phantoms with no identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't shoot me here, you're too naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for you to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
